Class SamplePerformanceMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • simulator.payloads.Networkable
      • simulator.framework.RuntimeMonitor
        • simulator.elevatorcontrol.SamplePerformanceMonitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TimeSensitive

    public class SamplePerformanceMonitor
extends RuntimeMonitor
    This monitoring class gives you a starting point for the performance checks you will do in project 7. This monitor detects the number of stops where the car becomes overweight when the door are open. Each stop counted at most once, unless the doors close completely and then reopen at the same floor. See the documentation of simulator.framework.RuntimeMonitor for more details.
